Package: php-jalismrs-bitwarden
Version: 1.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>
Installed-Size: 34
Depends: php-common, php-symfony-process (>= 6.0), php-symfony-process (<< 7~~), php-cli
Recommends: bw-cli
Section: php
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/jalismrs/bitwarden-service.php
Description: PHP services to access Bitwarden data via CLI
 This library provides PHP classes for interacting with the
 Bitwarden CLI (bw) to manage vault items programmatically.
 It supports authentication, session management, and searching
 vault items through a delegate-based service architecture.
